&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;269&quot; data-end=&quot;292&quot;&gt;Join us at GUSTOVENTURA&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;446&quot; data-end=&quot;799&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gustoventura.de/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;446&quot; data-end=&quot;462&quot;&gt;Gustoventura&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;offers authentic, innovative, and sustainable travel experiences across the &lt;strong data-start=&quot;539&quot; data-end=&quot;561&quot;&gt;Mediterranean area&lt;/strong&gt;, including &lt;strong data-start=&quot;573&quot; data-end=&quot;611&quot;&gt;Italy, Spain, Greece, and Portugal&lt;/strong&gt;. Our tours immerse travelers in the essence of each destination through unforgettable experiences, strong connections to local culture, and a focus on regional food, wine, and traditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;801&quot; data-end=&quot;1064&quot;&gt;As a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;806&quot; data-end=&quot;841&quot;&gt;Tour Conductor for Gustoventura&lt;/strong&gt;, you will help our travelers fulfill their dream of discovering the Mediterranean, creating meaningful and memorable journeys by bridging cultural gaps and fostering an appreciation for local, seasonal culinary traditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;801&quot; data-end=&quot;1064&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: The team is currently full, but the team is fast-growing, and we might have opportunities soon! Please keep in mind, we&#39;ll only consider applications written in English.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1121&quot; data-end=&quot;1124&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1126&quot; data-end=&quot;1139&quot;&gt;Your Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1141&quot; data-end=&quot;1258&quot;&gt;As a Tour Conductor, you will lead small groups (maximum 12/16 travelers) on &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1209&quot; data-end=&quot;1257&quot;&gt;1–2 week tours across the Mediterranean area&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
