&lt;li&gt;International &amp;amp; friendly working environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quarterly&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/venturatravelteam/&quot;&gt;Social Days and Team Events&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
