&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are engage

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Join us at Ventura TRAVEL – a group of specialized travel brands based in Germany that unleash the adventurer in every person! VIVENTURA offers authentic, innovative, and sustainable travel experiences in South America&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;(Peru).&lt;/strong&gt; We want our customers to enjoy the beauty of the continent while experiencing unique and unforgettable adventures.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As our Tour Conductor for VIVENTURA you will accompany our clients in their dream of discovering beautiful Peru, as well as making their trip an unforgettable lifetime experience! You will join our team of passionate Tour Conductors and report to our Tour Conductor Operations Specialist for &lt;strong&gt;VIVENTURA&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;David Thebaud&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Note: we will only consider applicant that submit a resume and that answers all the application questions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On daily basis, you will&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as VIVENTURA host, day-to-day guide, interpreter, and manager to a group of Senior travellers (small size 06-12 people) on a 02-03 weeks all-country (and multi-countries) trip&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide leadership for our travelers and be responsible for their well-being, ensuring their safety and operating a smooth tour.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain the established travel itinerary as closely as possible, making changes only when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep calm even when it gets stressful, act according to the protocol in special circumstances, and provide flexible solutions on your own.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make sure that the services delivered by our partners meet our quality, safety, and sustainable standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep track of everyday spending, save receipts, and keep expenses under the specified trip budget.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our clients are more than just customers to you; you treat them like friends and make sure their trip with us will be the best experience they can have.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Simply having a good time and sharing it with people from French-speaking countries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The basics you bring along&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced knowledge (C2 level) of the &lt;strong&gt;English&lt;/strong&gt; language for communication with clients. Plus, you are fluent in &lt;strong&gt;Spanish&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have all the right permissions to work/guide in Peru&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a first Aid Certification (CPR and Heimleich manoeuvre)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive knowledge (and continually increase) of Peru as a travel destination and the passion to show it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are interested in sustainable, local &amp;amp; authentic travel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are engaging, reliable and well organized.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good health, high energy level and positive attitude. We need TC&#39;s who can always handle the daily stresses, both mental and physical, of long and tiring days.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are the friendly, happy and helpful face of VIVENTURA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practical experience using internet, e-mails and google platforms and a smartphone able to run Android 14 or above or IOS 13 or above&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You can impress us even more with&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good English language communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous working experience as TC and/or guide, specially in Peru.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
